Orange May Be in Talks to Buy S. Africa’s BCX, TechCentral Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-09-08T11:50:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/orange-might-be-in-talks-to-acquire-south-africa-s-bcx-techcentral-says.html
France Telecom SA (FTE) ’s Orange unit may
be in talks to buy South Africa’s  Business Connexion Group Ltd. (BCX) ,
TechCentral reported, citing three people in the industry that
are familiar with the talks who it didn’t identify.  BCX Chief Executive Officer Benjamin Mophatlane and an
unidentified Orange spokesman based in France declined to
comment, the Johannesburg-based news website said. The industry
people do not work for either BCX or Orange, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  